23 North Dakota or other participating lender to repay outstanding student loan principal
24 balances for eligible applicants. The maximum annual student loan repayment grant
25 amount for which an applicant may qualify is five thousand six hundred sixty-seven
26 dollars, or one-third of the applicant's outstanding student loan principal balance upon
27 initial application for the program, whichever is less. The maximum total student loan
28 repayment grant amount for which any applicant may qualify is seventeen thousand
29 dollars.
